Installation instructions and usage information can be found under the
"Installation & Setup" section of the TMDA homepage:

    <URL:http://tmda.sourceforge.net/>

A local copy of the HTML documentation is included in the "doc"
directory.

If you are upgrading from an earlier release of TMDA, make sure to
consult the `UPGRADE' file.

To report success:
  % ( python -c 'from TMDA.Defaults import *; print DELIVERY_AGENT' ) \
    | mail jason-tmdausage@mastaler.com

